briefTitle: Evidence Based Dissemination for Mammography Adherence in Safety Net Communities
officialTitle: Evidence Based Dissemination for Mammography Adherence in Safety Net Communities
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Underserved as defined by income \<=200% of the federal poverty level for a family of four
* Uninsured
* In need of mammography screening; has received clinical breast exam and referral to screening
* Has upcoming screening appointment

Exclusion Criteria:

-
